  description: "functools.partial.__repr__ qualname=='partial.__repr__' (len 16), class 'wrapper_descriptor'; __new__ qualname=='partial.__new__' (len 15), class 'builtin_function_or_method'; partial.__name__=='partial'; wave 261; new to extra134"
